    "title": "Yohana, Mwana wa Zebedayo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "yohana, mwana wa zebedayo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Yohana alikuwa mmoja wa wale wafuasi kumi na wawili wa karibu zaidi wa Yesu (walioitwa mitume). Alikuwa kaka yake Yakobo na mwana wa Zebedayo. Yesu aliwachagua wanaume hawa kumi na wawili kama wawakilishi wake maalum na akawapa mamlaka ya kuwafundisha wengine kumhusu. Kazi yao ilisaidia kuanzisha kanisa la awali. Mapokeo ya awali yanasema Yohana, mwana wa Zebedayo, aliandika Injili ya Yohana, Barua za Yohana, na Kitabu cha Ufunuo.</p><p>Yohana na kaka yake Yakobo walikuwa miongoni mwa wafuasi wa karibu wa Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:37\">Marko 5:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:2\">9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:3\">13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:33\">14:33</a>). Mama yao, Salome, huenda alikuwa dada wa Maria, mama wa Yesu (linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:56\">Mathayo 27:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:40\">Marko 15:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1\">16:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:25\">Yohana 19:25</a>). Jina la Yohana mara nyingi huonekana baada ya Yakobo, ikionyesha kwamba Yohana alikuwa mdogo. Yakobo na Yohana walikuwa wavuvi kama baba yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:21\">Mathayo 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:19\">Marko 1:19</a>). Walivua samaki pamoja na Petro na Andrea, jozi nyingine ya ndugu waliokuwa wanafunzi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:8-Luke5:10\">Luka 5:8–10</a>).</p><p>Walikuwa miongoni mwa wanafunzi wa kwanza ambao Yesu aliwaita, na waliliacha kila kitu ili kumfuata (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:22\">Mathayo 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:20\">Marko 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:11\">Luka 5:11</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:35-John1:40\">Yohana 1:35–40</a>). Yesu aliwapa jina &quot;Wana wa Radi&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:17\">Marko 3:17</a>). Jina hili linaweza kumaanisha kuwa walikuwa na sauti kubwa au walikuwa na hasira ya haraka (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:54\">Luka 9:54</a>). Wakati mmoja, ndugu hao waliwakera wanafunzi wengine kwa kuomba nafasi maalum katika ufalme ujao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:20-Matt20:28\">Mathayo 20:20–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:35-Mark10:45\">Marko 10:35–45</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:24-Luke22:27\">Luka 22:24–27</a>).</p><p>Watu wanaamini Yohana ndiye &quot;mwanafunzi Yesu aliyempenda&quot; asiyejulikana na &quot;mwanafunzi mwingine&quot; aliyetajwa katika injili ya Yohana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:23-John13:25\">Yohana 13:23–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:15-John18:16\">18:15–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:26-John19:27\">19:26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:2-John20:10\">20:2–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:20-John21:24\">21:20–24</a>). Inawezekana alikuwa mwanafunzi asiyejulikana wa Yohana Mbatizaji ambaye, pamoja na Andrea, alikua mfuasi wa mapema wa Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:35-John1:40\">Yohana 1:35–40</a>).</p><p>Jina la Yohana linatajwa mara tatu katika Matendo. Kila wakati, anashirikiana na Petro (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:1-Acts3:11\">Matendo 3:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:1-Acts4:23\">4:1–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:14-Acts8:25\">8:14–25</a>). Paulo alimuita mmoja wa &quot;nguzo&quot; za kanisa huko Yerusalemu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:9\">Wagalatia 2:9</a>). Hii inaonyesha kwamba Yohana alikuwa kiongozi muhimu katika kanisa la Yerusalemu.</p><p>Desturi maarufu zaidi kuhusu maisha ya baadaye ya Yohana ni kwamba alihamia Efeso, ambako hatimaye alikua askofu wa Asia Ndogo. Aliishi hadi uzeeni na alikufa kwa amani miongoni mwa marafiki. Injili ya Yohana inatoa picha ya kina ya Yesu, na barua zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John5:21\">1 Yohana</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:1-2John1:13\">2 Yohana</a>, na <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:1-3John1:14\">3 Yohana</a>) zinatoa mtazamo wa kuvutia wa maisha ya Kikristo.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:21-Matt4:22\">Mathayo 4:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:2\">10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:1\">17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:20-Matt20:24\">20:20–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:37-Matt26:46\">26:37–46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:19-Mark1:20\">Marko 1:19–20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:29\">29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:17\">3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:37\">5:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:2\">9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:38\">38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:35-Mark10:41\">10:35–41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:3-Mark13:4\">13:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:33-Mark14:42\">14:33–42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:10\">Luka 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:14\">6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:51\">8:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:28\">9:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:49\">49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:54\">54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:23-John13:25\">Yohana 13:23–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:15-John18:16\">18:15–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:26-John19:27\">19:26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:2-John20:10\">20:2–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:2\">21:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:7\">7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:20-John21:24\">20–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:13\">Matendo 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:1-Acts3:11\">3:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:1-Acts4:22\">4:1–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:17-Acts5:42\">5:17–42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:14-Acts8:25\">8:14–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:9\">Wagalatia 2:9</a></p>",
